Deployed the model within a Django web application for real-time fraud detection with user-uploaded data.

projects.name: Paytm Clone

Employed MongoDB for database management, Node.js and Express.js for server-side development, React.js and Redux for responsive user interfaces, and implemented WebSocket (socket.io) for real-time stock updates.
